dataset.title: Two new species and a new record of hydroids (hydrozoa: hydroidolina) from Port Phillip, Australia

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Watson, Jeanette E. (2016): Two new species and a new record of hydroids (hydrozoa: hydroidolina) from Port Phillip, Australia. Memoirs of Museum Victoria 75: 1-5, DOI: 10.24199/j.mmv.2016.75.01, URL: https://museumsvictoria.com.au/collections-research/journals/memoirs-of-museum-victoria/volume-75-2016/pages-1-5/
